Noto.title: Noto
Noto.byline: Noto is a city in Sicily, Italy, one of the eight world heritage listed "Late Baroque Towns of the Val di Noto".

Notodden.title: Notodden
Notodden.byline: Notodden is a town and municipality (kommune) in Telemark County, in East Norway.

Noto Peninsula.title: Noto Peninsula
Noto Peninsula.byline: Noto Peninsula (能登半島 Noto-hantō) is in Ishikawa prefecture, Japan.

Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes.title: Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes
Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes.byline: Notre-Dame-de-Lourdes is a hamlet of about 700 people (2016) in the Pembina Valley of Central Manitoba.

Nottingham.title: Nottingham
Nottingham.byline: Nottingham is a city in England, affectionately known as the "Queen of the Midlands".

Nottinghamshire.title: Nottinghamshire
Nottinghamshire.byline: Nottinghamshire is a county in the East Midlands of England.

Notre-Dame-du-Mont-Carmel.title: Notre-Dame-du-Mont-Carmel
Notre-Dame-du-Mont-Carmel.byline: Notre-Dame-du-Mont-Carmel is a charming locality in Lower-Mauricie, on the north shore of the St. Lawrence River, in the regional county municipality of Les Chenaux, in Mauricie.

Notre-Dame-des-Monts.title: Notre-Dame-des-Monts
Notre-Dame-des-Monts.byline: Notre-Dame-des-Monts is a municipality in the Quebec Region, on the north shore of the St. Lawrence River, in Quebec.
